<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="ceremony-n">ceremony <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'serəməni/    美 /'serəmoʊni/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-c">1.★ <strong>[C] 仪式；典礼：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>the opening / closing ceremony
开/闭幕式</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a graduation / wedding ceremony 
毕业/结婚典礼</p></div>

<h4 id="2u">2.<strong>[U] 礼节；礼仪：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>There is too much ceremony at official dinners.
正式宴会上礼节太多。</p></div></div>